Source.Name: glances
Source.Summary: Glances is a cross-platform system monitoring tool written in Python
Source.Description: Glances is a cross-platform monitoring tool which aims to present a large amount of monitoring information through a curses or Web based interface. The information dynamically adapts depending on the size of the user interface.
